                        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M5.07 19H19a2 2 0 001.75-2.96L13.75 4a2 2 0 00-3.5 0L4.25 16.04A2 2 0 005.07 19z"/></svg>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium" :class="darkMode ? 'text-gray-300' : 'text-gray-700'">PDF tidak dapat ditampilkan di browser ini</p>
